Reasoning: The paper discusses the design of software components, generators, and metalanguages, which are all related to software engineering (cs.SE). It also uses information theory to analyze the efficiency of communication in programming languages, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also touches on the cognitive difficulty of using abstraction mechanisms, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software design (cs.SD).
